typeDescriptions.typeString: function (uint256[3] memory,uint256[3] memory) view returns (uint256[3] memory)

statements.operations:
{
    let dm := 0
    dwPtr := mload(0x40)
    mstore(0x40, add(dwPtr, 512))
    loop:
    jumpi(loop_end, iszero(d))
    jumpi(even, iszero(and(d, 1)))
    dm := mod(d, 32)
    mstore8(add(dwPtr, i), dm)
    d := add(sub(d, dm), mul(gt(dm, 16), 32))
    even:
    d := div(d, 2)
    i := add(i, 1)
    jump(loop)
    loop_end:
}
